---
layout: content-page.njk
title: Blog
description: Insights on AI automation, workflow design, and building systems that run your business.
eyebrow: Blog
headline: Dispatches from the machine room.
sub: What we learn building AI systems for real businesses.
backLink: /
permalink: /blog/
---

{% if collections.blog.length %}
<div class="blog-list">
  {% for post in collections.blog %}
  <a class="blog-item" href="{{ post.url }}">
    <div class="blog-item-title">{{ post.data.title }}</div>
    <div class="blog-item-date">{{ post.date | isoDate }}</div>
    {% if post.data.excerpt %}<div class="blog-item-excerpt">{{ post.data.excerpt }}</div>{% endif %}
  </a>
  {% endfor %}
</div>
{% else %}
<p class="page-sub" style="margin-bottom:0">Nothing published yet. Check back soon.</p>
{% endif %}
